# Citron Design System

This project uses `@citron-systems/citron-ds` as the design token source. All styling should reference tokens from `src/styles/tokens.scss`.

## Token Aliases

- **Accent**: `--color-lime`, `--color-lime-light`, `--color-lime-dark`
- **Semantic**: `--color-text-primary`, `--color-bg-primary`, `--color-border-focus`
- **Spacing**: `--space-1` through `--space-32` (maps to `--inkblot-spacing-*`)
- **Typography**: `--font-size-*`, `--font-weight-*`, `--line-height-*`
- **Radius**: `--radius-sm` through `--radius-full`
- **Transitions**: `--transition-fast`, `--transition-smooth`

## For rgba() with tokens

Use RGB variables: `rgba(var(--color-lime-rgb), 0.1)` or `rgba(var(--color-error-rgb), 0.2)`.

## Direct citron-ds tokens

When needed, use raw `--inkblot-*` variables from the package (see `node_modules/@citron-systems/citron-ds/dist/css/inkblot-variables.css`).
